citeinfo.title: Public Land Survey System (PLSS) Townships, Itasca County, Minnesota

descript.abstract: This dataset represents the PLSS Townships for Itasca County. The Itasca County PLSS data is based on the best and most current survey records available. This data is used to create the parcel dataset. Data users should be aware that Itasca County is continually updating this dataset. Updates to this dataset are expected as horizontal control positions from GPS are added.
descript.purpose: This data is a key component of the PLSS framework upon which parcel boundary information is assembled.

timeperd.current: The data set is complete, but is being continually updated as better positional accuracy becomes available.

dataqual.complete: The PLSS Townships are complete, with the exception of: T14728W, T14628W

attracc.attraccr: All attribute values have been verified by the Department of Surveying and Mapping.

procstep.procdesc: The PLSS positions, as shown, were determined using Global Position Systems and traditional survey measurements in a least squares adjustment. Interior corner positions and unrecovered PLSS corner positions were established using acceptable survey methods.

dataqual.logic: GIS software checks are performed for topological consistency. This ensures there are no duplicate lines, gaps, overlaps, undershoots, or overshoots.
